title: Proposal to continue the Bunny Boost and BUNNY-BNB Boost pools.
body:
Thanks to the incredible support of the community, we have been able to continue growing strong even through the recent challenges of migration!  As a special thank you, Team Bunny would like to propose a vote to mint BUNNY to extend our Bunny Boost and Bunny-BNB Boost Pools for 4 more weeks!

Period: 5/6 11:00 UTC - 6/3 11:00 UTC (4 weeks)
